songs.title: Lonely Road/Geneva
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Intro]
Hey, hey
Hey

[Verse 1]
I just fucked my ex bitch, pull up on the next bitch
Like what's on your necklace, please open your legs, bitch
No, I'm not your daddy, bitch, but I can be your daddy, bitch
Grab me like [?], bitch, really wanna focus on the addy, bitch
Know your daddy mad at you, real bad bitch, with an attitude
Middle school was fuckin' you, really mad a nigga was cuffin' you
Way to make a nigga uncomfortable-

[Chorus]
So I'm to go, as we walk this lonely road-
